        </item>
        <item>
            <title>PS5 Slim 外國拆機，散熱設計更完善</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/ps5-slim-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-slim-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/ps5-slim-3/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 10:10:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Slim]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203180</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 全新 PS5 Slim 即將於 11 月 10 日在美國率先推出。不過離推出前 5 日，YouTube 上已出現 PS5 Slim 評測，稱 PS5 Slim 的新設計比 PS5 小很多。</p><p>外國頻道「Dave2D」早前在 YouTube 上載名為「全新 Sony PS5 「Slim」-拆解+感想」的影片。展示 PS5 Slim 的修長機身，而全新的主機外殼則採用半啞光半亮面設計，共分為 4 部分，因此用家不能將 PS5 的主機蓋套用至 PS5 Slim 上。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40-694x374.png" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40-694x374.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40-1280x690.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40-768x414.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40-1536x828.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.28.40.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Dave2D 在片中特別提到 PS5 及 PS5 Slim 的重量差異，數碼版及光碟版 PS5 分別重 3.3 公斤及 3.9 公斤，而 PS5 Slim 則分別重 2.6 公斤及 3.2 公斤。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02-694x350.png" alt="" width="694" height="350" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02-694x350.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02-1280x645.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02-768x387.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02-1536x774.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-07.22.02.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Dave2D 指出，PS5 Slim 以 PS5 的主機內部機構作基礎，再加以小調整，以延續 PS5 主機內部機構的設計概念。PS5 及 PS5 Slim 皆利用主機上半部中間的鼓風扇散熱。不過 PS5 Slim 的 M.2 NVMe SSD 轉移至風扇後方，而光碟機位則安置在主機右下方的護蓋下，用家只需開啟護蓋便能可拆卸光碟機位。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07-768x403.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.15.07.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於 PS5 Slim 的內部散熱功能，亦如 PS5 般採用兩面配置的散熱器。配備 5 條導熱管及 2 塊散熱片的液態金屬熱介面散熱器則用作處理晶片，而負責 VRM 供電迴路的散熱分別裝有 1 條導熱管及 1 塊散熱片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38-768x403.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.17.38.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>為了提升散熱效率，所有 PS5 Slim 的散熱片皆圍著風扇四周，M.2 NVMe SSD 亦更貼近鼓風扇，以增加機身內的冷卻氣流。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50-768x403.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/螢幕截圖-2023-11-06-09.26.50.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>雖然 Sony 為 PS5 及 PS5 Slim 用家提供橫向使用的底座，但縱向使用 PS5 Slim 的用家則需另外加購底座。 Dave2D 又指由於新機功耗略高，因此推算 PS5 Slim<b></b>沒有採用新晶片。</p><p>Sony 早前曾表示，預計今年聖誕節將是有史以來遊戲機銷售最好的季節之一。因此 PS5 在自 2020 年 11 月推出以來，首次出現供多於求的情況。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63040"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tCGZ6pkbD5E?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/the-ps5-slim-is-not-that-much-smaller-than-its-chunkier-sibling-according-to-this-new-teardown-video">Eurogamer</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/ps5-slim-3/fun-tech/">PS5 Slim 外國拆機，散熱設計更完善</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
